public class Source
extends Object
implements Serializable

This class represents an Atom 1.0 source element.

Author:
Bill Brown 
        atomSource =
          element atom:source {
          atomCommonAttributes,
          (atomAuthor*
          & atomCategory*
          & atomContributor*
          & atomGenerator?
          & atomIcon?
          & atomId?
          & atomLink*
          & atomLogo?
          & atomRights?
          & atomSubtitle?
          & atomTitle?
          & atomUpdated?
          & extensionElement*)
          }

Atom Syndication Format, Serialized Form
